08/02/2011
TIRANA, Albania -- Police seized 1 tonne of marijuana Tuesday (February 8th) near Gjirokastra, in southeast Albania.
The operation, code-named "Co-ordinates", intercepted the haul on the national road leading to Greece.
One person was arrested, while warrants were issued for three others.
(Top News, Balkan Web, Top Channel - 08/02/11)
